@startuml ViewReviewComments
left to right direction
skinparam style strictuml

actor Developer

boundary "Review Comments Page" as ReviewUI
control "Review Controller" as ReviewCtrl
entity "Review Comments" as CommentData

Developer --> ReviewUI : view comments
ReviewUI --> ReviewCtrl : fetchComments()
ReviewCtrl --> CommentData : getReviewData()
ReviewCtrl --> ReviewUI : return comments
ReviewUI --> Developer : display feedback

@enduml
